Interface IAeMessageContext

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
IAeExtendedMessageContext
All Known Implementing Classes:
AeExtendedMessageContext, AeMessageContext
public interface IAeMessageContext
extends java.io.Serializable

Provides the context for an inbound message to the bpel engine.

getEmbeddedEndpointReference

public IAeWebServiceEndpointReference getEmbeddedEndpointReference()
Deprecated. Deprecated. Use getPartnerEndpointReference() instead.

Gets the embedded endpoint reference that should be used for any asynchronous replies on this partner link. This is an optional value and is only used if the endpoint reference source for the partner link is declared as "invoker" in the PDD.

getPartnerEndpointReference

public IAeWebServiceEndpointReference getPartnerEndpointReference()
Deprecated. Deprecated. Use getWsAddressingHeaders().getReplyTo() instead.

Gets the embedded endpoint reference that should be used for any asynchronous replies on this partner link. This is an optional value and is only used if the endpoint reference source for the partner link is declared as "invoker" in the PDD.

getMyEndpointReference

public IAeWebServiceEndpointReference getMyEndpointReference()
Deprecated. Deprecated. Use getWsAddressingHeaders().getRecipient() instead.

Gets the endpoint reference that was invoked or null if not set.

getProcessVersion

public java.lang.String getProcessVersion()
Gets the version of the process that the message is targeting. A null or empty string indicates that the message should be routed to the current version of the process.

getBusinessProcessProperties

public java.util.Map getBusinessProcessProperties()
Accessor for name/value properties that will be passed to the business process instance.
